@startuml
title Request Quotation Activity Diagram

start
:Customer opens Goods/Services flow;
:Select product category and item;
:Enter dimensions or quantity;
if (Input valid?) then (yes)
  :Calculate price;
  :Show estimate summary;
  if (Customer finishes quote?) then (yes)
    :Build estimate order model;
    :Generate estimate PDF;
    :Send quotation document;
    stop
  else (no)
    :Continue quotation flow;
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  :Prompt for corrected input;
  stop
endif

@enduml
